_sText:
CS:GO Vertigo layout with CS:S texture, models and custom resource to fit a bit the original map.
Isn't finished and more updates will come.

The beta release is just the basic, map was compiled in fast so, some visual lightning issues will be expected as for bugs too. 

Please if you download the maps, report some big bugs, glitchs that affect gameplay. Some bugs and issues i've know:

- Helicopter without animations

- Crane with arm not extended

- Some props cliping through the floor

- No radar 

- C4 missed if fall from the map
